title: Athlete of the Week - Macki Walsh
text:
slideshow 
Macki Walsh - Etowah - Cross CountryMacki Walsh won the individual title and led Etowah to the team championship at the Cherokee County cross country meet last Saturday.Walsh won the girls race in 19 minutes, 26.74 seconds and paced an Etowah team that finished five runners in the top 10. How long sheâ€™s run cross country: Eight years Favorite thing about the sport: The connection with her team and the pride she feels when her team wins Favorite color: Yellow Favorite food: Anything having to do with peanut butter Favorite movie: McFarland, USA Favorite musical artist: Twenty One Pilots Dream vacation: Traveling from mountain to mountain and skiing with friends Dream car: A light-yellow Volkswagen bug Favorite sports team: Georgia
